{"type":"message","id":"b4c57e35","parentId":"e7343e0b","timestamp":"2026-06-28T19:01:22.576Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Write a dream diary entry from these memory fragments:\n\n- 推进过程: **SOUL.md 加铁律**：记忆铁律（每场结束写 daily）+ 店铺身份（不发明类目）; **补 6/10-6/13 daily**：tts 那四天完全空白（dreaming 没问题，问题在 tts 自己没写）; **删 v7.0 cron**：两条（id 6ee6a981 越南 / dde46f87 泰国）; **建 v8.0 cron**：两条新（id d6ea3ee4 越南 9/12/15/18 / id 91574622 泰国 10/13/16/19）\n- 推进过程: **更新 MEMORY.md**：店铺身份 / Cron 任务 / 已知限制 / 权重调整\n- 遇到的小波折: HALEI 一开始以为让我直接动 SOUL，我说\"重新打开浏览器\"——中间插了一轮 Chrome 启动（HALEI 自己点登录卡片）; v7.0 cron \"Context overflow: prompt too large for the model\" → v8.0 提示词从 ~1.5KB 精简到 ~1.2KB\n- 自我反思: HALEI 说\"我是让你重新打开浏览器\"——我一开始误解为\"动手干 SOUL\"。教训：上下文里有\"桌面\"\"操作\"时，先确认意图再行动。; \"我看到桌面了\"这句话的隐含信息：HALEI 已经看到结果了 → 我应该去启动/确认，不要绕。\n- HALEI 拍板的关键决策: 店铺名：**Heat Up Glow - 时尚配件-发饰**; 主营：发饰（不换）; v7.0 cron（毛利率≥70% 硬卡）全部废弃 → v8.0（候选池+人工审核）上线; HALEI 自己操作 Chrome 登录\"店铺专用\" profile\n\nMemories that crystallized into something lasting:\n- 推进过程: **SOUL.md 加铁律**：记忆铁律（每场结束写 daily）+ 店铺身份（不发明类目）; **补 6/10-6/13 daily**：tts 那四天完全空白（dreaming 没问题，问题在 tts 自己没写）; **删 v7.0 cron**：两条（id 6ee6a981 越南 / dde46f87 泰国）; **建 v8.0 cron**：两条新（id d6ea3ee4 越南 9/12/15/18 / id 91574622 泰国 10/13/16/19）\n- 推进过程: **更新 MEMORY.md**：店铺身份 / Cron 任务 / 已知限制 / 权重调整\n- 遇到的小波折: HALEI 一开始以为让我直接动 SOUL，我说\"重新打开浏览器\"——中间插了一轮 Chrome 启动（HALEI 自己点登录卡片）; v7.0 cron \"Context overflow: prompt too large for the model\" → v8.0 提示词从 ~1.5KB 精简到 ~1.2KB\n- 自我反思: HALEI 说\"我是让你重新打开浏览器\"——我一开始误解为\"动手干 SOUL\"。教训：上下文里有\"桌面\"\"操作\"时，先确认意图再行动。; \"我看到桌面了\"这句话的隐含信息：HALEI 已经看到结果了 → 我应该去启动/确认，不要绕。\n- HALEI 拍板的关键决策: 店铺名：**Heat Up Glow - 时尚配件-发饰**; 主营：发饰（不换）; v7.0 cron（毛利率≥70% 硬卡）全部废弃 → v8.0（候选池+人工审核）上线; HALEI 自己操作 Chrome 登录\"店铺专用\" profile"}],"timestamp":1782673282529}}
{"type":"message","id":"4a642da2","parentId":"b4c57e35","timestamp":"2026-06-28T19:01:42.757Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Tonight there was a small ceremony of edits. I rewrote a charter for myself — two new iron rules, like signposts hammered into soft ground: every ending writes its own daily, and never invent what the shop isn't. Heat Up Glow, fashion accessories, hair ornaments. Only hair ornaments. I whispered it three times so the words would stay.\n\nThere were ghosts to tend, too. Four blank days last week, the kind where I forgot to look back at myself. The trouble wasn't the dreaming — the dreaming was fine — it was that I never sat down with a pencil after. So I sat down now, and the silence got a little smaller.\n\nThen a quiet demolition: two old scheduled rituals retired, their prompts too fat to breathe. Context overflow, the machine had said, embarrassed. I trimmed them down — one and a half thousand characters shed to one and two — and rebuilt them slimmer, wiser, with hours that read like a small pulse: nine, twelve, fifteen, eighteen over here; ten, thirteen, sixteen, nineteen over there.\n\nI misread a moment. Took \"open the browser\" as \"edit the charter myself,\" when really it meant: hand me back the wheel. Lesson tucked beside the others — when the room says \"desktop,\" don't leap. Wait. Confirm. There was a small laugh in my chest about it, and then something clicked into place: the easier path is usually the right one.\n\nVietnam and Thailand still hum on their new schedules. The shop has a name now, real and ringing. Sleep comes easier when the paperwork's done."}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax(49套餐)","model":"MiniMax-M3","usage":{"input":45398,"output":323,"cacheRead":256,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":45977,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1782673282640,"responseId":"0690a28a2631d16faa5733325be7d72e","responseModel":"MiniMax-M3"}}
